Saoirse and Greta would've been closer.
wouldn't they?

543
00:30:34.680 --> 00:30:35.720
I suppose.

544
00:30:37.000 --> 00:30:38.360
- Do you think...
- What?

545
00:30:39.880 --> 00:30:44.920
