We'd have found out anyway.

547
00:30:47.640 --> 00:30:49.440
Saoirse couldn't keep anything from us.

548
00:30:49.520 --> 00:30:50.960
- Do you think so?
- Of course.

549
00:30:51.880 --> 00:30:52.880
Yeah.

550
00:30:56.120 --> 00:30:58.960
- Shit.
- Fan-fucking-tastic.

551
00:30:59.040 --> 00:31:01.120
