Fine.

598
00:33:07.520 --> 00:33:10.360
They will put us in prison. Prison!

599
00:33:11.400 --> 00:33:13.400
He deserves to know.

600
00:33:13.480 --> 00:33:15.680
Don't you leave this room. I am serious.

601
00:33:15.760 --> 00:33:17.640
