All good here. thank you. Lucy.

649
00:36:29.560 --> 00:36:31.520
So what is this. some sort of sex thing?

650
00:36:31.600 --> 00:36:32.560
It is. yes.

651
00:36:32.640 --> 00:36:35.720
- Do you Belfast ones have no shame?
- It would appear not.

652
00:36:35.800 --> 00:36:38.360
Dirty bitches.

653
